data.description: Take a look at this lovely townhouse in Lewisville! It's super convenient, close to Highway 121. Ready to move in, it has two bathrooms, two bedrooms, and a flexible study that could also be a third bedroom or an office. It's one of the bigger homes around here with an open layout and a fenced backyard—great for relaxing or BBQs. There's a community pool nearby, and the HOA looks after the yard work. Plus, you get a fridge, washer, and dryer with the house. Don't miss out on this great neighborhood!
